Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这枚镜片借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去弄清楚那个叫做坂井悠二的人是否是火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你现在这个样子实在帮不上我什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小姑娘你这样在这个城市出生长大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实地保留了城市的本来面目的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于调律来说是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果坂井同学是火炬的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的祭典上 我要向坂井同学表白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为得到悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“化装舞会”很有可能会潜入这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里本来就失去了平衡 会进一步恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再待在这个城市里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有“化装舞会”来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已经不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天要和妈妈 和其他人分别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过再让我在这儿平平常常地多待一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天穿上单衣和服让悠二大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一起去参加祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到哪天要离开这里的时候 也要一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和我一起离开这个城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着迷到这种地步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们明白这意味着什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的目标是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使这把刀了 就会带上我们了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不是拐弯抹角地叫我们不要跟着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常温柔嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是平时的你 肯定狠狠地揍一顿了事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子明天要下酒雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 穿上单衣和服参加祭典吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 买了一件新的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说离开这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究还是很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究还是很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 今天五点后在桥对面会合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那位小姑娘不知道怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望那个叫作坂井悠二的男人不是火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 希望能冷静到可以协助我们的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市的调律稍微有些麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 扭曲得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在这里也做个标记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再安一两个应该就足够调律用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是扭曲 还有一种不和谐感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展很顺啊 至今为止一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 离完成准备工作还有6小时14分32秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我想的一样 这种花纹和你很相配
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到这么漂亮的小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠肯定会大吃一惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小悠他也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我做好了离开城市的思想准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有些伤感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周六一般不是下午开始训练的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很早回来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他说了今天是晚上开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我没告诉他我要去参加祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是闲逛去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲逛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜 我们一起去找小悠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定碰巧遇到了池他们 正在游玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写张留言条的话 就是错过了也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边巧遇的话或许会更让小悠喜出望外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜 看 那就是苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠在祭典的日子里一定要买的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想尝尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍我们训练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是来参加祭典的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人说要出门 男的就该闭上嘴跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那样子继续练下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会成为难看的生人片了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣太 去买点酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全没意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多摊位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有卖苹果糖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道坂井同学有没有出事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就会一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剩下的就是等待那位小姑娘的协助了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是这种不和谐感令人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是扭曲得太厉害的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有徒的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个时候也没有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 人类也能予以利用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被任何一个火雾战士察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授 已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后对坂井同学说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:11:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才都一点气息也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草 我忽然想起还有事情 你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒 徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有自在式却没气息又是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在哪里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之散心就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去玻璃坛那里就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把徒的藏身之处找出来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熟练了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做法都知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 不会真打算带上他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是利用一下他们那股傻劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以往一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有用玻璃坛搜查的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这个自在式还真是庞大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此手法 绝非等闲之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二也应该已经察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先去找夏娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么吉田一美会和悠二在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吉田同学知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是火炬这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点追的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随她去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随她去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧 徒开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可得好好向吉田同学说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二必须跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要和吉田一美解释
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随她去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无关？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉田一美完全无关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是毫无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到夏娜会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说并不是毫无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣装驱逐者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好久不见 天壤劫火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也对这自在式...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可西亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这个乱七八糟的自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有种不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 “追根究底”但他林
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那个疯教授
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一点都没那家伙的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样或许更要依靠玻璃坛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快啊 啓作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中那个家伙去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学 什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不告诉我刚才和你在一起的那个女人是谁我就不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 只是个熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敷衍我 你在说谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学 我要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然之间提起这事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常地...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢田中荣太你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁给你那个东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒已经展开攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我们接着刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这个自在式使扭曲加剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市就将被无法修复的巨大的扭曲所吞没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为了什么而做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有对策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只要进行调律就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要的标记已经安置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有对这城市的本来面目有印象的助手在...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 其实对于人选我们也心中有数了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有些许麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个叫作“吉田一美”的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她身上的气息原来是你们的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她过来的话 马上就能进行调律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我去把她带来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会达成身为火雾战士的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士们差不多该来碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米诺 知道怎么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 开始第二阶段作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我有点过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不能马上给你回复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之待会儿我会来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能在封绝中活动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 得想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.98,0:22:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 热闹起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后会怎么发展 值得期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到教授的行踪之时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.34,0:24:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御崎市上空正在完成的“灵魂殿堂”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.14,0:24:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜以一名火雾战士的身份在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.53,0:24:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边想着渐行渐远的悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.35,0:24:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.19,0:24:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗之中
